title: Oracle Database: Recovery Area
agents: linux, solaris, hpux
catalog: app/oracle
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 Checks the used space in the recovery area of an Oracle database. Reclaimable
 space is considered as free hereby. The default levels for warn/crit are at
 70% and 90% of used space.

item:
 The ORACLE_SID

inventory:
 One service is created for each database.
